sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Browser
    participant View as CalendarView
    participant DB as Database
    participant Model as WydarzenieKalendarzowe (Polymorphic QuerySet)
    participant Google as Google Calendar

    %% =========================
    %% OPEN CALENDAR
    %% =========================
    User ->> Browser: Open "Kalendarz"
    Browser ->> View: GET /kalendarz/

    View ->> Model: Query upcoming events
    Model ->> DB: SELECT * (polymorphic join)
    DB -->> Model: Wydarzenie + Chrzest records

    Model -->> View: Unified queryset of events

    View -->> Browser: Render calendar page (KW-10)

    Browser -->> User: Display list of upcoming events

    %% =========================
    %% SUBSCRIBE TO CALENDAR
    %% =========================
    User ->> Browser: Click "Dodaj do Google Calendar"

    Browser ->> View: GET /kalendarz/subscription/

    View ->> Model: Get events for calendar feed
    Model ->> DB: Fetch event data
    DB -->> Model: Event records

    Model -->> View: Event dataset

    View ->> View: Generate ICS / subscription feed (KW-11)

    View -->> Browser: Return calendar feed / link

    Browser ->> Google: Open / subscribe to calendar feed
    Google -->> User: Calendar added / subscribed
